genitals, the

00:05:53.439 --> 00:05:54.599
clitoris, the labia, and in severe cases,
the wound that's left is sewn

00:05:54.599 --> 00:06:07.909
up, so there's only a tiny hole left.
I'm just pleased the day is here, actually,

00:06:07.909 --> 00:06:11.180
because it's been a lot of
prep to get to this point.

00:06:11.180 --> 00:06:16.389
It's night one in Davos and as you can see,
it's absolutely beautiful.

00:06:16.389 --> 00:06:22.520
My belief is that issues like this can't stay
on the margins, that they

00:06:22.520 --> 00:06:24.199
really have to be debated at the highest levels.

00:06:24.199 --> 00:06:26.090
